/*
Leetcode 206 : Reverse Linked List

Apporach 1 : iterative method 
--> Time Complexity : O(n);
--> Space complexity : O(1);

Approach 2 : Recurrsive method 
--> Time Complexity : O(n);
--> Space Complexity : O(1);
*/

# Iterative Method 
